messages = Array[String](["Half unaware of where you’re going you find yourself in Grimshire's red light district.", "You’ve been here before, interviewing people for the newspaper. It’s a dangerous place full of junkies, dark alleys and more importantly; no police.", "This is the forgotten part of town, the other Grimshire. The part people don’t talk about. ", "Vesper: If I’m really considering becoming a prostitute maybe I should try the hospital first? I’m sure it has some IV bags I could take without anyone noticing.", "Vesper: I shouldn't be here! How can I even think about doing something like this?", "Vesper: A few months ago, the bus was so crowded, a guy rubbed against me the entire way to work, and I couldn’t say anything. ", "Vesper: When I was leaving… I felt something squeezing my butt. I can’t prove it, but I know it was him. I hate when people touch me where they shouldn’t.", "Vesper: But, If I had the guts to start selling my body… I could easily find targets here. Just look at that woman over there. She looks pretty happy with that client touching her breasts.", "Vesper: And why wouldn’t she be? He just paid for five minutes of her time more than what I make in a whole day!", "Vesper: With that kind of money I could start a savings account, quit my regular job, and move somewhere else less sunny. ", "Vesper: Besides, I can’t keep making excuses not to show up to work when the sun’s out. It’s a matter of time before somebody at the newspaper starts getting suspicious. Or worse…", "Vesper: Depending on how much money I make as a prostitute, with my frugality, I’d able to retire in a few years.", "Vesper: Maybe I wouldn’t even have to do much… I could take them to a dark alley, let them touch me a little, and when their guard is down, suck the life out of them. ", "Vesper: Plenty of money and all the blood I can drink. Isn’t this the perfect plan? I’d be killing two birds with one stone.", "Vesper: What am I thinking? Have I stooped so low to be even considering that? I love my job… even if the payment isn’t what I expected.", "Vesper: I’m better than this… I should consider other options first, not jump into something out of desperation.", "Nonetheless, the hunger inside you begs to differ.", "Vesper: I’m so hungry!!! I would do anything for a drop of blood! Anything...... maybe even......", "Vesper: No! If I stay here I might end up doing something I regret... ", "Vesper: I should leave before I get more ridiculous ideas.", "--- NOT FIRST VISIT BUT NOT MASTURBATED ---", "You find yourself once more visiting the red light district.", "Vesper: I know what happens in this place. I’ve seen it with my own eyes. If I stay here I’ll end up just like them.", "However, you can feel your fangs throbbing inside your mouth, begging to come out. Like an assassin’s dagger, refusing to be sheathed, yearning for fresh blood.", "Vesper: It hurts so much! I have to do something, anything to stop this pain!", "Vesper: I’ve watched porn before, I’m not dumb. Handjobs, blowjobs, footjobs, titjobs, If I promise a customer any of those things, I can get him alone and… ", "Vesper: AaaaAAhH, this hunger is driving me insane! I can barely control my thoughts. If anyone tries to touch me right now, I might end up killing them on the spot.", "Vesper: Can I even feel anything besides hunger? I’m a terrible actress. If I approach someone in this state they’ll know something’s wrong.", "Vesper: I have to relax, get to know my body first. Only then, I can consider…... selling it, without risking ripping someone’s throat open the first chance I get.", "Vesper: I should go home for now. It’s not safe for me to be here. ", "Vesper: Besides, I still have other options, don't I? ", "With that hammering in your mind you decide to leave.", "-- END OF NOT MASTURBATED AND NOT FIRST VISIT --"])

